{"tid":1772794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 我自豪","createTime":"2019-12-07T03:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T03:34:33.000Z","uid":215909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45d17a29149119acca45eadcb23a6631cedc3945","tid":1772794,"uid":215909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:13:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1772471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1772471</a><br />\n睇完呢篇文有感而發<br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時，我覺得好善忘，但我都估唔到香港人可以堅持咁耐，我以為遊行最多遊一兩個月就會收皮，然後條例通過，返工嘅返工，返學嘅返學。香港人一直創造奇蹟，呢幾個月大家寫下屬於我哋自己嘅歷史，好多謝大家一齊行落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋128再創造奇蹟</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">128見！！！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8b7b420db838bee4f28cfc775563dd7dbce44e74","tid":1772794,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">128 維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"eb4bb9d96d3a5b53e8dd56ffeb6086807ed41100","tid":1772794,"uid":30678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8lRkjNbA1ms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8lRkjNbA1ms&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=af9663be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8lRkjNbA1ms</a><br />\n<strong>就趁我們難得一起再聚不要退</strong>"},{"pid":"5005f27fbeefcb12a6f8ace2dd21cde5342ae28b","tid":1772794,"uid":215909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"推爆128<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}